		"Name": "Grasshopper",
		"Details": "Introduced in 3063, the GHR-6H is a new production attempt to go after the Stealth medium mech hunter concept from the original GHR-4R.   Utilizing a Light Fusion Engine sourced from the Lyrans as well as Pafftek Industry and the RAD Group's efforts in Composite Endo-Carbide structure, as well as Stealth Armor appropriated from the House Liao backed insurgents.   The GHR-6H is a bit of a monster on the battlefield.  The weapon load consists of a Streak LRM5 launcher in the head with 1/2 ton of ammunition in a CASE2 protected torso as well as 1 ER Large laser for long range sniping and 4 medium lasers for in close killing.   While giving up some potential for maximal damage the GHR-6H makes up for it in superior all around survivability in spite of the larger engine.  A total of 14.5 tons of Stealth Armor protech the chassis.\n\n <b><color=#e51717>Pafftek Industries Sub-mod</color></b>",
